d": "16_1674175404.4581478", "card_id": "Q_579378162", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国内多地发布提醒要警惕疟疾，其症状和新冠相似，或危及生命，两种疾病的区别是什么？它们之间有关联吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "伴随新冠病毒感染「乙类乙管」、出入境政策调整和我国传统佳节春节的临近，海外华人入境返乡较为集中，大量境外旅游、劳务人员回国下飞机就可以直接回家吃团圆饭了！但是团圆的同时也要注意国内多地发布提醒警惕疟疾。 疟疾和新冠的相似症状有两点： 一是都以发热为主要表现， 二是部分新冠有腹泻症状，部分恶性疟患者主要表现也有腹泻。甚至，在疟疾特别是恶性疟的临床表现中，规律地畏寒寒颤通常并不明显，而常以头痛、乏力、腹泻、恶心、呕吐等为主要表现。 多地紧急提醒！和新冠症状相似，小心出现漏诊或误诊，或危及生命"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-477299b53b61320b6670746f4fd2e819_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "50 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579378162"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IltTm89yyragSEAMaCDkxMDMyMzI1INCenp4GMAc4gAJAEHIJNTc5Mzc4MTYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1674175404.4589198", "card_id": "Q_579022285", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 57}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "内马尔是不是近二十年最差的巴西头牌?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "带队成绩几乎为 0"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-633e31abfde97c5c149f945ee7b7a62a_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/579022285"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IltTm89yyragSEAMaCDkwOTUzMTI1ILifk54GMAU4fkARcgk1NzkwMjIyODV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1674175404.459514", "card_id": "Q_579086916", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 75}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价剧版《三体》中的原创角色慕星？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "其实我是喜欢杨蓉的，这个角色目前真的是喜欢不起来…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dff1f11795963f04aa02704325c5c51d_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_a